      <num>Section 601</num>
      <heading>Compensation</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The city manager shall be paid a salary commensurate with the city manager's responsibilities
               as chief administrative officer of the city, which salary shall be established by
               ordinance or resolution.</p>
        <p>(As amended June 3, 1980.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
